Author: speakofthewolf
Text: One of many dumb BS things the medical industry does. Like... you could drop dead for ED behaviors irregardless of your BMI... they must know that, right? You deserve help now.

Author: princess-kitty-belle
Text: I'm sorry that you had this experience, emergency departments are notorious for being invalidating for people who aren't at a deathly BMI. Please know that you are worthy of help.
